<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.6.10">
<l>akkākkāy nampikkuk kōlkoṇṭu vāveṉṟu</l>
<l>mikkā ḷuraittacol villiput tūrppaṭṭa</l>
<l>ṉokka vuraitta tamiḻpattum vallavar</l>
<l>makkaḷaip peṟṟu makiḻvariv vaiyattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master [these] ten Tamil [verses]</l>
<l>spoken harmoniously by the scholar of Villiputtūr</l>
<l rend="indent">on the words, “Caw! Caw! Bring a staff for the prince!”,</l>
<l rend="indent">spoken by the Great Lady,</l>
<l>will beget children [and] rejoice in this world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
